V`20he
Xwon,`20he`20will`20use`20the`20opening`20roll`20and`20his`20ldb`20will`20send
Xyour`20ldb
Xa`20message`20telling`20you`20how`20he`20moved.`20`20Either`20way,`20the`20gam
Ve`20is`20off
Xand`20running.
